items.title: Fashionably Pink benefit kicks off Phoenix Fashion Week
items.summary:
Phoenix Fashion Week’s signature Fashionably Pink Celebrity Fashion Show, powered by Tal Barkel, sponsored by Tuft & Needle, Kendra Scott, & DigitalWire360, benefiting local breast cancer non-profit Don’t Be a Chump! Check for a Lump! kicks off Thursday, October 5th. Phoenix Fashion Week organizers are thrilled to introduce an exciting new host venue for the 2017 event: The beautiful outdoor 80-foot-long, poolside runway at Talking Stick Resort. “Our entire team here at Don’t Be a Chump!
